text: Events from the year 1105 in Ireland. ==Incumbents== *High King of Ireland: Domnall Ua Lochlainn ==Events== *Cellach Ua Sinaig inherits the position of Abbot of Armagh (the seventh in a series of members of the Ua Sinaig family, who had held the position without taking holy orders, and several of whom had been married). ==References==
title: 1105 in Ireland
